OL,3,CUK inflation unchanged at 2.2%, above
OL,4,CBank of England's target
OL,6,FUK inflation has remained unchanged at
OL,7,F2.2% in August, the Office for
OL,8,FNational Statistics said, just above
OL,9,Fthe Bank of England's 2% target.
OL,11,FDespite staying steady for the second
OL,12,Fmonth in a row, price pressures picked
OL,13,Fup pace in the key services sector as
OL,14,Fair fares jumped higher.
OL,16,FInflation rose for the first time this
OL,17,Fyear in July.
