OL,6,FThe ONS said services sector inflation
OL,7,Fjumped to 5.6% in August from 5.2% in
OL,8,FJuly as air fares rose across European
OL,9,Froutes.
OL,11,FThis offset falls in prices at petrol
OL,12,Fpumps.
OL,14,FThe figures come ahead of the Bank of
OL,15,FEngland's next interest rate decision
OL,16,Fon Thursday.
