OL,4,CBank of England's target
OL,6,FGrant Fitzner, chief economist at the
OL,7,FOffice for National Statistics, said:
OL,8,F"Inflation held steady in August as
OL,9,Fvarious price fluctuations offset each
OL,10,Fother.
OL,12,F"The main movements came from air
OL,13,Ffares, in particular to European
OL,14,Fdestinations, which showed a large
OL,15,Fmonthly rise, following a fall this
OL,16,Ftime last year.
OL,18,F"This was offset by lower prices at
OL,19,Fthe pump as well as falling costs at
OL,20,Frestaurants and hotels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
