OL,3,CUK inflation unchanged at 2.2%, above
OL,4,CBank of England's target
OL,6,FWhile inflation in the sector is
OL,7,Fvolatile, it has been stubbornly high
OL,8,Fand has been watched closely by Bank
OL,9,Fpolicymakers.
OL,11,FThe Bank itself has forecast that
OL,12,Fservice inflation is set to pick up
OL,13,Fthis autumn before falling back again
OL,14,Fby the year-end.
OL,16,FThe figures are unlikely to persuade
OL,17,Fpolicymakers to vote for another rate
OL,18,Fcut this month after last month's
OL,19,Freduction to 5% from 5.25%.
