OL,3,CUK inflation unchanged at 2.2%, above
OL,4,CBank of England's target
OL,6,FDarren Jones, Chief Secretary to the
OL,7,FTreasury, said: "Years of sky-high
OL,8,Finflation have taken their toll; and
OL,9,Fprices are still much higher than four
OL,10,Fyears ago.
OL,12,F"So, while more manageable inflation
OL,13,Fis welcome, we know that millions of
OL,14,Ffamilies across Britain are
OL,15,Fstruggling, which is why we are
OL,16,Fdetermined to fix the foundations of
OL,17,Four economy so we can rebuild Britain
OL,18,Fand make every part of the country
OL,19,Fbetter-off."
